{"id":1735106,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:16.315Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735106,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Namaku Bedah","overview":"# My Name Is Bedah  The story follows Bedah (Aishah Azman), an intelligent and nimble girl who possesses a fickle personality and is always keen to show off. Her beautiful face has attracted many suitors, but they mock her when they learn her real name and make it the subject of ridicule. Bedah is a combination of her mother's and father's names as terms of endearment—Hamidah and Bedul. After completing her schooling, Bedah continued her studies at college. At college, Bedah becomes the center of attention for many male students. Some even lose sleep and get into fights just to win her heart. One day, Bedah accidentally meets Zuhairi (Nadzmi Adhwa), the son of a famous wealthy businessman. Bedah is mesmerized by Zuhairi's handsomeness. It turns out Bedah's feelings are reciprocated, as Zuhairi is also interested in her. Knowing Zuhairi's status, Bedah uses an alias—Princess Anis. Bedah becomes so excited that everything she does goes wrong.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/2EiFQb5yBCoLa3j277uM6Q3CIpD.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Namaku Bedah","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1752536,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Aishah Azman","original_name":"Aishah Azman","popularity":0.1309,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5ec1cd7e1dede173bb4dff","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1265337,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Niezam Zaidi","original_name":"Niezam Zaidi","popularity":0.6331,"profil